footer: The emerald is so unique and stunning while the band is elegant, petite, and classic. The combination is exactly what I dreamed my engagement ring would be. I am over the moon with joy to wear it for the rest of my life. — Ang

Instead of a diamond, I went with a gorgeous peachy-pink morganite and I couldn't be happier. I love the color of the stone and how it looks with the Luxe Viviana band. I am beyond pleased with my ring. — Lindsey
This ring met all of my expectations. It is so light and dainty, but looks so luxurious especially with the sapphire gemstone. — Kayleigh
